  "tips": [
    "Climb to the summit of Mont-Né via the Crête de la Pale to enjoy a 360° panorama of the highest peaks of the Central Pyrenees (departure from Port de Bales: we say hello to the cows on the way!!! 😊)",
    "The Pic du Mont-Né offers an exceptional view and is quite accessible from the Col de Bales.",
    "The Cromlechs of the Pyrenees are comparatively modest megalithic structures in a circular shape with diameters between about 2.0 and a little more than 10.0 meters and stones that very rarely reach a height of 3.0 m. The origin is dated to 1200 to 600 BC. Dated.",
    "Clean, spacious, well equipped, rescue from thunderstorms with hail"
